{"tid":1491174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Freshman 同我入黎] 呼籲各位罷去各大專院校既迎新日/著黑衫去","createTime":"2019-08-20T10:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T10:29:46.000Z","uid":20694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d343f9d7a14a91c75d4f77ef74016744dcc77e13","tid":1491174,"uid":20694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"睇到隔離台有個post 呼籲各位罷去各大專院校既迎新日，所以想搞大佢<br />\n<br />\n各位手足 希望大專生可以罷去所有迎新日 作為9月罷課既前哨<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日 有唔同手足準備左片去回顧呢兩個月既運動 我諗我地每個人 都會睇到眼濕濕 因為當中有人因為呢個運動離開 有人受傷 有好多人被捕 ...... 已經過左2個幾月 政府唔回應 黑警越來越黑 如果我地唔再加大力度 跟本唔可以對抗個政府<br />\n<br />\n所以 希望大家唔好參加迎新日 或者如果返去既 請著黑衫同上台講5大訴求 為9月罷課 增加d動力<br />\n<br />\n願有天煲底脫下口罩相見 <br />\n<br />\nHeung Kong Yan Ga Yau!"},{"pid":"72aa5fd93af1bfac888c6f83321c6889a5eac362","tid":1491174,"uid":20694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0635c230c58e91c01c56342aa085e49c1b5018b3","tid":1491174,"uid":20694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"307ab0ed21600b86b0533d9eac49198741eeae4c","tid":1491174,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"願有天煲底脫下口罩和底褲一齊裸跑"},{"pid":"ddb240ebcd79f6aa8cc5ad9bf2940f22b2d313b7","tid":1491174,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"(626)(醫管局cctv)黑警醫院虐打62歲老人20min片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LamCheukTing.Official/videos/695076584288759/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLamCheukTing.Official%2Fvideos%2F695076584288759%2F&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9qf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=b8759f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LamCheukTing.Official/videos/695076584288759/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/imr7pj2h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fimr7pj2h&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9qf05AUSLZ